---
title: Pistachio-Crusted Chicken with Quinoa and Chopped Cucumber Jalapeño Salad
description: Have you had enough of quinoa yet? Good, neither have we. This time, we’ve topped the wholesome grain with pistachio-crusted chicken, a refreshing cucumber and tomato salad, and a bit of jalapeño for good measure. Because if there’s one thing that never gets old, it’s a bright and cheery dish that’s both good and good for you.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pistachio-crusted-chicken-w49-9d8962cc.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/pistachio-crusted-chicken-w49-a44816f8.pdf
servings: 2
course: main course
cuisine: North America
time required: 30 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 570 kcal
  fat: 18 g
  saturated fat: 2 g
